#11702
The Mud School~
&WNow, to leave the mud school at any time, just go up.
When you see an &Oorange&W word in a room description while
learning, that is a reference on something to type.  If a word is in
<> such as "<item>" then you replace the <> and the inner word(s) with
a substitute word, in this case the name of an item on you or on the
ground, etc.  The orange word is usually capitalized, and commands do
not need to be capitalized in order to work.
To begin with you were given a weapon (now equipped on you) and a player's
guide.  Typing "&OLOOK BOOK&W" will give you a list of help topics to
refer to for information on a subject.
~
