#11705
Preparation for the Academy~
&WThe purpose of the academy is to train your character through fighting
the creatures that lurk inside.  The first thing you will want to do
in the academy is to go to the practice room where you can learn to use
skills and/or spells available to your class.  See "&OHELP PRACTICE&W" for
more on that.  When you battle the mobiles in the academy, some will
give you gold while others will give you certain miscellaneous pieces of
equipment from armour to leggings.  Some things can be done with config
like autoloot, meaning after you kill something you automatically take
everything from it's corpse, and autosac which will sacrafice the creature
for favor (see "&OHELP FAVOR&w") and a bit of extra gold.  See "&OHELP
CONFIG&W" for more on configuration.  If you don't config autoloot, you
will have to manually get items from it's corpse, see "&OHELP GET&W" to
learn to do that.
~
