#11706
Preparation for the Academy pt. II~
Having left off with getting equipment from the creature's corpse, you
will now have to equip the item to make use of it.  See "HELP WEAR" for
the syntax of the "wear" command and related commands.
The academy is not an entirely easy place for many people, on your way
down into the lower areas of it where you will encounter the beasts, you
will notice a statue called the Adept of Kyorin.  The room where this
stands is a safety room where no creature can move into, and the adept
has healing powers which it will cast on you to help you recover.  Look
at the adept when you encounter it to learn more on how to recover stats.
Return there often between battles so you can safely heal and will take
less risk of getting killed.  See "HELP DEATH" for some pointers on
dying in Amethyst.  Also please note lastly that every time you go down a
level the monsters will get tougher and tougher, so be sure that you're
capable, and bring a light too, like a torch, for it is often too dark to
see in the lower depths.
~
