#11707
An example in fighting~
&WHere is an example of a creature you will come across in the academy.
A simple Imp, it is stationary, waiting in specific spots to engage
attack with someone wandering the academy first basement floor.  They can
be tricky if you were to be attempting to make it outside having been injured
seriously, and as such can be quite formidable.  Again, see "&OHELP COMBAT&W"
for help on initiating and doing battle.  You may continually fight this
mobile as many times as you can stand, but just don't overdo it and
get killed...
~
