#11800
At the end of the mud school~
&wNow you have learned about everything that you will need to learn
to at least begin the real game, and hopefully pass through the academy.
The very last things to mention are the commands &CTYPO&w, &CBUG&w, and 
&CIDEA&w.  These three commands we put together so that people can give
us feedback if we've missed something.  Please read the helpfiles on
them and use them if necessary.  Under "idea" you may put in a request
should there be something that has been overlooked in this tutorial.
Also you may make use of the MMMB (Main Mortal Message Board) to post notes
on to fellow mortals and immortals alike, which is located at the "Post
Office" just southwest of Town Square in New Hope.
~
